description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Warren Vache is a supremely accomplished, versatile and rare performer. He has been astounding audiences worldwide for decades with his superb cornet, trumpet and flugelhorn stylings. Here, he gives a basic lesson on embouchure in your trumpet playing.
